full_text:
Hi Juli,

Thanks for your input -- this is interesting -- could it be that Mike 
and Lisa use these fragments in conjunction with psycho-kinesis in 
order to modify the tone of these fragments to sound as their own 
voices would have sounded when they were alive?  We know they don&#39;t 
have vocal cords, and so they probably communicate via some kind of 
thought/mind process ...  Not to say that all the entities employ 
this method, maybe some of the more identifiable ones like Mike and 
Lisa.

I love mulling over things and this will keep me mulling for quite a 
long time.

Sharon the Muller


